description:
Put your defense and strategic skills to the ultimate test in the new Tournament Mode! Defend your base from the never ending waves of enemies and compete with your friends in weekly tournaments! Play for as long as you can survive!

Take charge of your army and defend the tower against advancing waves of enemies! Toy Defense is the ultimate simulation experience where you are the one to make the decision and build the line of defense. Lead you army to victory by any means!

Use different types of upgradable units available in your arsenal and place them in strategic points along the routes of enemy tanks, transporters and airplanes. Deflect multiple attacks, eliminate foes, improve your strategy and become a truly great leader!

Welcome to the world of Toy Defense, tower defense at its finest!
